Taylor Steele's newest video Momentum: Under The Influence. Set in exotic locations such as Mentawai Island, Australia, South Africa, France, Timor Island, Indonesia, Mexico, Hawaii and California. This video encompasses explosive surfing from around the world. Momentum: Under The Influence highlights a new breed of surfers taking the steps toward making surfing history. See who is leading the path in the years to come. Proceeds from the sale of the VHS will be donated to the World Trade Center Relief Fund. Proceeds from the sale of the DVD will be donated to the Jesse Billhauer Fund.Starring CJ Hobgood, Dan Malloy, Mick Fanning, Bruce Irons, Taj Burrow, Damien Hobgood, Joel Parkinson, Ben Bourgois, Andy Irons, David Rastovich, Dean Morrison and more. The DVD version allows you to watch the movie to 3 different soundtracks - Original, Punk, & DJ. You pick!
